casebody.data:
Wednesday, March 11, 1998

MERIT DOCKET

95-550. State ex rel. George v. Internal Revenue Serv.

In Mandamus. On response to show cause order and on motion for temporary restraining order and preliminary injunction. Sua sponte, cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur. Douglas, J., dissents.
